items.description:
It seems like you shouldn't be able to see a black bar in space. Doesn't black absorb all light?
```
  {black|_____________}
{gray|/}{black|/____________/}{gray|/}
```
{lemonchiffon|Requires a reset:}
1. Press *Max* and *Gain Instant* to produce as many black bars as possible.
2. Then, do *Black Bar Reset*.

Loosely pulls colors together, effectively separating them into large collections. Order black fabric in a texture that defines this force.

{lemonchiffon|When completed:}
• Configure [this location](/configure/location/44) to check *Show in Overview*.

